Reflections on Making Our New Essential Oils for Root Chakra Healing Videos

Author: Elizabeth Ashley
Date: 19 August 2025
Publisher: The Secret Healer
Canonical URL: Reflections on Making Our New Essential Oils for Root Chakra Healing Videos

Overview

This blog post reflects on crafting four YouTube videos blending aromatherapy, healing practices, and grounded chakra work—highlighting practices like vetiver, chamomile, and bee shamanism, and including intros to grounding, emotional tuning, and energy alignment through essential oils.

